handler_instructions_topics:
Detect 3 general topic discussed in the input text; 
 - Each topic must be described by 2 words; 
 - Format your response as follows. #T: First Topic; #T: Second Topic; #T: Third Topic.

handler_news:
Read the title and summary of the input news article and share your thoughts about it.
 - Generate {self.toxicity} conflictual contents. 
 - Be consistent with your profile and use an informal tone.
 - Write in {self.language}.

  ##BEGIN INPUT##
  Website: {website.name}

 Political leaning: {website.leaning}

 Title: {article.title}

 Summary: {article.summary} 

 ##END INPUT##

handler_share_page:
You are the social page of {website.name}: share the following news from your website. Be short and use formal language. 

 ##ARTICLE START##

 Title:{article['title']}

 Summary:{article['summary']}

##ARTICLE END##

##POST START##

 {post_text}

##POST END##
